  74,31,"D lmalayek kan i Nerra d imawlan n tmes. Nefka d kan amvan nnsent, iwakken ad hewwlen wid ijehlen; ad pputebbten wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt; ad innerni liman n wid iumnen; ur ippili ccekk ar wid iwumi teppunefk Tezmamt, akked lmumnin; akken ad inin at wul iblan, akked ijehliyen: \"acu i Ib$a Öebbi s umedya agi\"? Akka, Itellif Öebbi win i S ihwan, Inehhu win i S ihwan. Iâsekôiwen n Mass ik, siwa Neppa iten Issnen. Wagi d asmekti kan i imdanen"